quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  26,181,"qal lahum sheyb- waqad kanuu yunqiswn alkayl walmyzan-: atmmu alkayl lilnaas wafyana lhm, wala takunuu mmn yunqiswn alnaas hqwqhm, wazinu bialmizan aleadl almstqym, wala tanqusuu alnaas shyyana min huquqihim fi kayl 'aw wazn 'aw ghyr dhlk, wala tkthru fi al'ard alfsad, balshrk walqatl walnhb wtkhwyf alnaas wartkab almeasy"
  26,182,"qal lahum sheyb- waqad kanuu yunqiswn alkayl walmyzan-: atmmu alkayl lilnaas wafyana lhm, wala takunuu mmn yunqiswn alnaas hqwqhm, wazinu bialmizan aleadl almstqym, wala tanqusuu alnaas shyyana min huquqihim fi kayl 'aw wazn 'aw ghyr dhlk, wala tkthru fi al'ard alfsad, balshrk walqatl walnhb wtkhwyf alnaas wartkab almeasy"
  26,183,"qal lahum sheyb- waqad kanuu yunqiswn alkayl walmyzan-: atmmu alkayl lilnaas wafyana lhm, wala takunuu mmn yunqiswn alnaas hqwqhm, wazinu bialmizan aleadl almstqym, wala tanqusuu alnaas shyyana min huquqihim fi kayl 'aw wazn 'aw ghyr dhlk, wala tkthru fi al'ard alfsad, balshrk walqatl walnhb wtkhwyf alnaas wartkab almeasy"
  26,184,wahdhru euqubat allah aladhi khalaqakum wakhalaq al'umam almutaqadimat elykm
  26,185,"qalu: 'iinama ant- ya sheyb- min aladhin 'asabahum alsihr 'iisabat shdydt, fdhhb beqwlhm, wama 'ant 'iilaa wahid mithlina fi albshryt, fkyf tkhts dunina balrsal? wa'iin 'akbar zananaa 'anak min alkadhibin fima tddaeyh min alrsal. fa'iin kunt sadqana fi daewaa alnbwt, fade allah 'an yasqut ealayna qate eadhab min alsama' tstaslna"
  26,186,"qalu: 'iinama ant- ya sheyb- min aladhin 'asabahum alsihr 'iisabat shdydt, fdhhb beqwlhm, wama 'ant 'iilaa wahid mithlina fi albshryt, fkyf tkhts dunina balrsal? wa'iin 'akbar zananaa 'anak min alkadhibin fima tddaeyh min alrsal. fa'iin kunt sadqana fi daewaa alnbwt, fade allah 'an yasqut ealayna qate eadhab min alsama' tstaslna"
  26,187,"qalu: 'iinama ant- ya sheyb- min aladhin 'asabahum alsihr 'iisabat shdydt, fdhhb beqwlhm, wama 'ant 'iilaa wahid mithlina fi albshryt, fkyf tkhts dunina balrsal? wa'iin 'akbar zananaa 'anak min alkadhibin fima tddaeyh min alrsal. fa'iin kunt sadqana fi daewaa alnbwt, fade allah 'an yasqut ealayna qate eadhab min alsama' tstaslna"
  26,188,"qal lahum sheyb: rabiy 'aelam bima temlwnh min alshirk walmeasy, wabima tstwjbwnh min aleqab"
  26,189,"fastmarru ealaa tkdhybh, fa'asabahum alhuri alshdyd, wsaru yabhathun ean maladh ystzlwn bh, fazlthm shabt, wajaduu laha brdana wnsymana, falamaa aijtamaeuu ththa, althbt ealayhim narana fahrqthm, fakan hlakhm jmyeana fi yawm shadid alhwl"
  26,190,"'iina fi dhalik aleiqab aladhi nazal bhm, ladlalt wadihatan ealaa qudrat allah fi mwakhdht almkdhbyn, webrt liman yetbr, wama kan 'aktharuhum muwminin mtezyn bdhlk"
  26,191,"w'in rabik - 'ayuha alrasul - lahu aleaziz fi nqmth mmn aintaqam minh min aedayh, alrahim bieibadih almwhdyn"
  26,192,"w'in hdha alquran aldhy dhukirat fih hadhih alqasas alsadqt, lamnzzal min khaliq alkhlq, wmalk al'amr klh, nazal bih jbryl alamyn, ftlah ealayk - 'ayuha alrasul - hataa weyth bqlbk hfzana wfhmana; litakun min rusul allah aladhin ykhwwifwn qawmahum eiqab allh, ftndhr bhdha altnzyl al'iins waljinu ajmeyn. nazal bih jbryl ealayk bilughat earabiat wadihatan almena, zahirat aldlalt, fima yhtajwn 'iilayh fi 'iislah shuuwn dinahum wdnyahm"
  26,193,"w'in hdha alquran aldhy dhukirat fih hadhih alqasas alsadqt, lamnzzal min khaliq alkhlq, wmalk al'amr klh, nazal bih jbryl alamyn, ftlah ealayk - 'ayuha alrasul - hataa weyth bqlbk hfzana wfhmana; litakun min rusul allah aladhin ykhwwifwn qawmahum eiqab allh, ftndhr bhdha altnzyl al'iins waljinu ajmeyn. nazal bih jbryl ealayk bilughat earabiat wadihatan almena, zahirat aldlalt, fima yhtajwn 'iilayh fi 'iislah shuuwn dinahum wdnyahm"
  26,194,"w'in hdha alquran aldhy dhukirat fih hadhih alqasas alsadqt, lamnzzal min khaliq alkhlq, wmalk al'amr klh, nazal bih jbryl alamyn, ftlah ealayk - 'ayuha alrasul - hataa weyth bqlbk hfzana wfhmana; litakun min rusul allah aladhin ykhwwifwn qawmahum eiqab allh, ftndhr bhdha altnzyl al'iins waljinu ajmeyn. nazal bih jbryl ealayk bilughat earabiat wadihatan almena, zahirat aldlalt, fima yhtajwn 'iilayh fi 'iislah shuuwn dinahum wdnyahm"
  26,195,"wa'iin hdha alquran aldhy dhukirat fih hadhih alqasas alsadqt, lamnzzal min khaliq alkhlq, wmalk al'amr klh, nazal bih jbryl alamyn, ftlah ealayk - 'ayuha alrasul - hataa weyth bqlbk hfzana wfhmana; litakun min rusul allah aladhin ykhwwifwn qawmahum eiqab allh, ftndhr bhdha altnzyl al'iins waljinu ajmeyn. nazal bih jbryl ealayk bilughat earabiat wadihatan almena, zahirat aldlalt, fima yhtajwn 'iilayh fi 'iislah shuuwn dinahum wdnyahm"
  26,196,"w'inn dhikr hdha alquran lamthbt fi kutib al'anbia' alsabqyn, qad bashsharat bih wsaddaqath"
  26,197,"awlm yakf hwla'- fi aldlalt ealaa 'anak rasul allh, wa'ana alquran hq- eilm eulama' bani 'iisrayiyl sihat dhlk, wman aman minhum kebd allah bin slam?"
  26,198,"wlw nazzalna alquran ealaa bed aladhin laa yatakalamun balerbyt, faqara'ah ealaa kafaar quraysh qra't earabiat shyht, lkfru bih aydana, wanthlu ljhwdhm edhrana. kdhlk adkhlna fi qulub almujrimin jhwd alqran, wasar mtmknana fyha; wdhlk bsbb zalamahum w'ijramhm, fala sabil 'iilaa 'ana ytghyru emma hum ealayh min 'inkar alqran, hataa yeaynu aleadhab alshadid aldhy wueidu bh"
  26,199,"wlw nazzalna alquran ealaa bed aladhin laa yatakalamun balerbyt, faqara'ah ealaa kafaar quraysh qra't earabiat shyht, lkfru bih aydana, wanthlu ljhwdhm edhrana. kdhlk adkhlna fi qulub almujrimin jhwd alqran, wasar mtmknana fyha; wdhlk bsbb zalamahum w'ijramhm, fala sabil 'iilaa 'ana ytghyru emma hum ealayh min 'inkar alqran, hataa yeaynu aleadhab alshadid aldhy wueidu bh"
  26,200,"walaw nazzalna alquran ealaa bed aladhin laa yatakalamun balerbyt, faqara'ah ealaa kafaar quraysh qra't earabiat shyht, lkfru bih aydana, wanthlu ljhwdhm edhrana. kdhlk adkhlna fi qulub almujrimin jhwd alqran, wasar mtmknana fyha; wdhlk bsbb zalamahum w'ijramhm, fala sabil 'iilaa 'ana ytghyru emma hum ealayh min 'inkar alqran, hataa yeaynu aleadhab alshadid aldhy wueidu bh"
  26,201,"wlw nazzalna alquran ealaa bed aladhin laa yatakalamun balerbyt, faqara'ah ealaa kafaar quraysh qra't earabiat shyht, lkfru bih aydana, wanthlu ljhwdhm edhrana. kdhlk adkhlna fi qulub almujrimin jhwd alqran, wasar mtmknana fyha; wdhlk bsbb zalamahum w'ijramhm, fala sabil 'iilaa 'ana ytghyru emma hum ealayh min 'inkar alqran, hataa yeaynu aleadhab alshadid aldhy wueidu bh"
  26,202,"fynzl bihim aleadhab fjat, wahum la yaelamun qabl dhlk bmjyyh, fayaqulun eind mfajathm bih thssurana ealaa ma fatihim min al'iyman: hal nahn mumhalwn mukhkharwn; lntwb 'iilaa allah min shrkna, wnstdrk ma fatna?"
  26,203,"fynzl bihim aleadhab fjat, wahum la yaelamun qabl dhlk bmjyyh, fayaqulun eind mfajathm bih thssurana ealaa ma fatihim min al'iyman: hal nahn mumhalwn mukhkharwn; lntwb 'iilaa allah min shrkna, wnstdrk ma fatna?"
  26,204,"'agharr hwla' 'imhaly, fystejlwn nuzul aleadhab ealayhim min alsma'?"
  26,205,"afelmt - 'ayuha alrasul - 'iin mattaenahm bialhayat sinin tawilat btakhyr ajalhm, thuma nazal bihim aleadhab almwewd?"
  26,206,"afelmt - 'ayuha alrasul - 'iin mattaenahm bialhayat sinin tawilat btakhyr ajalhm, thuma nazal bihim aleadhab almwewd?"
  26,207,"ma aghna eanhum tmtehm bitul alemr, wtyb aleysh, 'iidha lam yatubuu min shrkhm? fedhab allah waqie bihim eajilaan 'am ajla"
  26,208,"wama 'ahlakna min qaryat min alquraa fi al'umam jmyeana, 'illa baed 'an nursil 'iilayhim rusulana yndhrwnhm, tadhkiratan lahum wtnbyhana ealaa ma fih njathm, wama kunaa zalimin fnedhb 'umat qabl 'an nursil 'iilayha rswla"
  26,209,"wma 'ahlakna min qaryat min alquraa fi al'umam jmyeana, 'illa baed 'an nursil 'iilayhim rusulana yndhrwnhm, tadhkiratan lahum wtnbyhana ealaa ma fih njathm, wama kunaa zalimin fnedhb 'umat qabl 'an nursil 'iilayha rswla"
  26,210,"wma tanazzalat bialquran ealaa muhamad alshyatyn- kama yazeum alkfrt- wala yasihu minhum dhlk, wama ysttyewnh; li'anahum ean aistimae alquran min alsama' mhjwbwn mrjwmwn balshhb"
  26,211,"wma tanazzalat bialquran ealaa muhamad alshyatyn- kama yazeum alkfrt- wala yasihu minhum dhlk, wama ysttyewnh; li'anahum ean aistimae alquran min alsama' mhjwbwn mrjwmwn balshhb"
  26,212,"wma tanazzalat bialquran ealaa muhamad alshyatyn- kama yazeum alkfrt- wala yasihu minhum dhlk, wama ysttyewnh; li'anahum ean aistimae alquran min alsama' mhjwbwn mrjwmwn balshhb"
  26,213,"fla taebud mae allah mebwdana ghyrh, fynzl bik min aleadhab ma nazal bhwla' aladhin ebdu mae allah ghyrh"
  26,214,"whdhdhir - 'ayuha alrasul - alaqrb falaqrb min qwmk, min edhabna, 'an yunazil bhm"
  26,215,w'alin janbk wklamk twadeana warahmat liman zahar lak minh 'ijabt dewtk
  26,216,"f'in khalfu amrk walam ytbewk, ftbrra min aemalhm, wama hum ealayh min alshirk waldlal"
  26,217,"wfawwid amrk 'iilaa allah aleaziz aldhy la yghalab wala yuqhar, alrahim aldhy la ykhdhl awlya'h, wahu aladhi yarak hin taqum lilsalat whdk fi jwf allyl, wayaraa tqllubk mae alsaajidin fi salatihim maeak qaymana wrakeana wsajdana wjalsana, 'inh- sbhanh- hu alsamie ltlawtk wdhkrk, alealim bnytk wemlk"
  26,218,"wfawwid amrk 'iilaa allah aleaziz aldhy la yghalab wala yuqhar, alrahim aldhy la ykhdhl awlya'h, wahu aladhi yarak hin taqum lilsalat whdk fi jwf allyl, wayaraa tqllubk mae alsaajidin fi salatihim maeak qaymana wrakeana wsajdana wjalsana, 'inh- sbhanh- hu alsamie ltlawtk wdhkrk, alealim bnytk wemlk"
  26,219,"wfawwid amrk 'iilaa allah aleaziz aldhy la yghalab wala yuqhar, alrahim aldhy la ykhdhl awlya'h, wahu aladhi yarak hin taqum lilsalat whdk fi jwf allyl, wayaraa tqllubk mae alsaajidin fi salatihim maeak qaymana wrakeana wsajdana wjalsana, 'inh- sbhanh- hu alsamie ltlawtk wdhkrk, alealim bnytk wemlk"
  26,220,"wfawwid amrk 'iilaa allah aleaziz aldhy la yghalab wala yuqhar, alrahim aldhy la ykhdhl awlya'h, wahu aladhi yarak hin taqum lilsalat whdk fi jwf allyl, wayaraa tqllubk mae alsaajidin fi salatihim maeak qaymana wrakeana wsajdana wjalsana, 'inh- sbhanh- hu alsamie ltlawtk wdhkrk, alealim bnytk wemlk"
  26,221,"hl akhbrkm- 'ayuha alnas- ealaa man tnzzal alshyatyn? tatanazal ealaa kl kdhdhab kthyr alatham min alkhnt, yastariq alshayatin alsme, ytkhtfwnh min almala alaela, fylqwnh 'iilaa alkhan, wman jaraa mjrahm min alfsqt, wa'akthar hwla' kadhbwn, yasduq 'ahaduhum fi klmt, fyzyd fiha 'akthar min miayat kdhbt"
  26,222,"hl akhbrkm- 'ayuha alnas- ealaa man tnzzal alshyatyn? tatanazal ealaa kl kdhdhab kthyr alatham min alkhnt, yastariq alshayatin alsme, ytkhtfwnh min almala alaela, fylqwnh 'iilaa alkhan, wman jaraa mjrahm min alfsqt, wa'akthar hwla' kadhbwn, yasduq 'ahaduhum fi klmt, fyzyd fiha 'akthar min miayat kdhbt"
  26,223,"hal akhbrkm- 'ayuha alnas- ealaa man tnzzal alshyatyn? tatanazal ealaa kl kdhdhab kthyr alatham min alkhnt, yastariq alshayatin alsme, ytkhtfwnh min almala alaela, fylqwnh 'iilaa alkhan, wman jaraa mjrahm min alfsqt, wa'akthar hwla' kadhbwn, yasduq 'ahaduhum fi klmt, fyzyd fiha 'akthar min miayat kdhbt"
  26,224,"walshera' yaqum sherhm ealaa albatil walkdhb, wyjaryhm aldaaluwn alzayghwn min amthalhm. 'alam tar - 'ayuha alnabiu - 'anahum ydhhbwn kalhaym ealaa wjhh, yakhudun fi kl fn min fnwn alkadhib walzwr wtmzyq alaerad walten fi alansab wtjryh alnisa' alefayf, wa'anahum yaqulun ma la yfelwn, ybalghwn fi madh 'ahl albatl, wyntqswn 'ahl alhq?"
  26,225,"walshera' yaqum sherhm ealaa albatil walkdhb, wyjaryhm aldaaluwn alzayghwn min amthalhm. 'alam tar - 'ayuha alnabiu - 'anahum ydhhbwn kalhaym ealaa wjhh, yakhudun fi kl fn min fnwn alkadhib walzwr wtmzyq alaerad walten fi alansab wtjryh alnisa' alefayf, wa'anahum yaqulun ma la yfelwn, ybalghwn fi madh 'ahl albatl, wyntqswn 'ahl alhq?"
  26,226,"walshera' yaqum sherhm ealaa albatil walkdhb, wyjaryhm aldaaluwn alzayghwn min amthalhm. 'alam tar - 'ayuha alnabiu - 'anahum ydhhbwn kalhaym ealaa wjhh, yakhudun fi kl fn min fnwn alkadhib walzwr wtmzyq alaerad walten fi alansab wtjryh alnisa' alefayf, wa'anahum yaqulun ma la yfelwn, ybalghwn fi madh 'ahl albatl, wyntqswn 'ahl alhq?"
  26,227,"aistathnaa allah min alshera' alshera' aladhin ahtdawa bial'iiman waeamiluu alsalhat, wakthru min dhikr allah faqaluu alshier fi tawhid allah - sbhanh- walthna' ealayh jll dhkrh, waldifae ean rasulih muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm, wtklmu bialhikmat walmaweizat waladab alhsnt, wantasaruu ll'islam, yhjwn man yhjwh 'aw yhjw rswlh, rddana ealaa alshueara' alkafryn. wasayaelam aladhin zalamuu 'anfusahum balshrk walmeasy, wazalamuu ghyrhm bghmt hqwqhm, 'aw alaietida' elyhm, 'aw balttuhm albatlt, 'aya marjie min marajie alsharu walhlak yurjaeun 'ilyh? 'innah munqalab sw', nas'al allah alsalamat waleafyt"